---
// Modern about section
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 bg-noise-grid"></div>
  <div class="absolute -left-8 top-24 text-7xl animate-bounce">🕺</div>
  <div class="absolute right-6 top-16 text-6xl animate-pulse">✨</div>
  <div class="absolute right-10 bottom-10 text-8xl animate-spin">💿</div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.55), transparent 18%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(0,0,0,0.08), transparent 22%);"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container-custom relative">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6 gradient-text">
          About The Legend
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-black">Every sentence is here to scream confidence and cause mild eye strain.</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left column - Description -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-xl text-black mb-6 leading-relaxed font-bold">
            Hello!!! I am Gourish Chouhan, software engineer, pixel wrestler, and full-time destroyer of boring layouts. I convert normal requirements into loud, energetic, impossible-to-ignore web experiences.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-black mb-6 leading-relaxed font-bold">
            My approach combines engineering, design instincts, and a dangerous amount of enthusiasm. I build with React, modern JavaScript, and enough CSS to make every viewport feel like it drank six energy drinks.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-black leading-relaxed font-bold">
            Currently leveling up through data structures, algorithms, and real-world products while maintaining a deeply committed relationship with over-the-top creative chaos. Respectfully: subtlety is not the brand today.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="chaos-chip">Certified Keyboard Smasher ⌨️</span>
            <span class="chaos-chip">UI Fireworks Specialist 🎆</span>
            <span class="chaos-chip">Professional Overthinker 🧠</span>
            <span class="chaos-chip">Possibly Too Online 📡</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ascii-panel mt-8 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            <pre>{String.raw`ME.EXE STATUS REPORT
--------------------
confidence: [##########]
restraint:   [#---------]
vibes:       [##########]
glitter css: [##########]`}</pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right column - Skills cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="card card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-gray-200 dark:group-hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">Full-Stack Wizardry</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-sm font-bold">
            Shipping frontends, backends, and dramatic entrances with React, Node.js, and databases.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-gray-200 dark:group-hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">Responsive Chaos</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-sm font-bold">
            Making loud interfaces behave on mobile, desktop, and whatever cursed screen size shows up.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-gray-200 dark:group-hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364-.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">Problem Obliteration</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-sm font-bold">
            Turning confusing bugs and weird requirements into something users can actually enjoy.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-gray-200 dark:group-hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">Turbo Vibes</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-sm font-bold">
            Balancing performance, polish, and totally unnecessary animation with suspicious confidence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
